 Denmark by DDEsubsidiary GMI Data.andP;  Once it has become established as a supplier to thenewspaper market, DDE Great Britain might extend its activities to othermarkets that use the DDE platform, such as CAD/CAM.andM;The UK management team is made up to executives from ND Comtec, poached byDDE in much the same fashion as they were originally poached by ND fromLinotype.andP;  Eddie Zubcov is now divisional manager at DDE Great Britain; TerryMcGinnie is sales manager; Mark Jobson is pre-sales support manager; and JohnMason is marketing manager.andM;To partially fill the void left at ND Comtec, Chris Jordan has joined thatfirm as sales director.andP;  He is well known in the industry for his work asmanaging director of Graphic Displays Ltd. and previously as marketingmanager at Linotype.andO;</TEXT></DOC>